Tumie Kopeka is a Writer (Scriptwriter), Radio and Television Content Developer, Creative Director, Broadcaster, a Network - Cyber Security IT Technician and a Mentor. His experience overall from Multichoice, Viacom Africa, Primedia, eMedia and SABC in Television Development, Directing, Pitching and Facilitating the discussion with focus on business, and media management, entrepreneur, Radio, Television and Digital. Marketing and ICT put him among the most smart Game Changer.
